{"tid":257321,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有文字直播]2016-17 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附四強次回合","createTime":"2017-05-25T07:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T02:05:02.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e82732ef4c9b5c02a5c7d3199dd39431701ab0","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附加賽四強次回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-5-25 7pm-12am *括號內數字為聯賽最終排名</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/y62ciOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy62ciOO.png&h=e05c5d4c&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5dBYP3n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5dBYP3n.png&h=bbe4d03d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(3)張曦雯vs劉佩玥(6)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合:12-5)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5Acncyz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5Acncyz.png&h=a7f96ea0&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/krRMKZI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkrRMKZI.png&h=8d9c4b3d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(4)文詠珊vs岑麗香(5)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合:9-9)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">升班附加賽四強賽時為五小時，會員可於指定時段於以回覆投票方式揀選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">會員需清晰指出賽事投選女神，亦可選擇性投票予心水賽事。如會員同時投予兩位參賽者，將視為會員選擇和局，不投票增加該場比賽任何參賽者分數。<br />\n為免影響比賽公正性及體驗，會員<span style=\"color: red;\">不能再次回覆</span>以<span style=\"color: red;\">修改或增加投票選項</span>，請考慮好心水決定才作回覆投選。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"f8d7c3bcb0a1407369e0a2d62dbc512c8c8a44db","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"為方便會員投選,大家可引用以下列表以便發佈投票選項<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附加賽四強次回合<br />\n2017-5-25 7pm-12am<br />\n張曦雯vs劉佩玥<br />\n文詠珊vs岑麗香"},{"pid":"d36057f7a734c8c450bef19d88b70e452ffbf97d","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:34:30.000Z","msg":"其餘升班附加賽賽程請參閱下址<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2e0deb403de2d14dd38b320e9000287638128a7b","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:08:50.000Z","msg":"兩場賽事既作客女神已經抵達比賽場館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f89d4902a358a22a4b190e45a51ccd5f8026648","tid":257321,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"請代投<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附加賽四強次回合<br />\n2017-5-25 7pm-12am<br />\n張曦雯<br />\n岑麗香"},{"pid":"f3673f721d7117dda614057ccba6f67d0ebceb33","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"張 劉<br />\n雙方進入比賽場地"},{"pid":"9356e6835807f6b2a96a0600aa088ce7b3c27099","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"文 岑<br />\n雙方進入比賽場地"},{"pid":"e6e8160948107f5cc656fdb4bcc12e5d1e2b5124","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"根據天文台,依家溫度係26度,濕度百分之77<br />\n係非常適合比賽既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de58f06705cec7d9bd4df7ce501cd1e21434b64","tid":257321,"uid":92376,"like":0,"